  "system": {
    "description": "<p>During a Quick Rest, you can magically bond with <strong>1 Weapon</strong> and choose an <strong>Elemental</strong> or <strong>Mystical</strong> damage type, this becomes your “Bound Damage”.</p><p>While you hold the Bound Weapon, it gains the following properties:</p><ul><li><p><strong>Illuminate:</strong> You can spend <strong>1 AP</strong> to cause it to emit Dim or Bright Light (you choose the light’s appearance) in a 5 Space radius. The light is extinguished if you release the Weapon or choose to do so for free.</p></li><li><p><strong>@UUID[Compendium.dc20rpg.classes.Item.9bYRAL9nuk21Z5NZ]{Smite}</strong></p></li><li><p><strong>Recall:</strong> While the Weapon is within 20 Spaces, unheld, and unsecured, you can call your Weapon back to you for free, causing it to fly to you. If you don’t have a free hand when you call it, or you choose not to grab it, it falls in your Space at your feet.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Ending Early:</strong> Your bond with the Weapon ends early if you use this Feature again or you choose to end it for free.</p>",
